&lt;li&gt;Certified in IPC-610, IPC-620, J-STD and other assembly and inspection standards.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in building test cables, including crimping contacts, soldering connectors, and reading wiring diagrams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience using ECAD viewers (Altium, Eagle, OrCAD, etc.) to locate components on a board layout.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Environmental testing: Familiarity with thermal chambers, vibration tables, and burn-in procedures.&lt;/li&gt;
